completed rules:

1) 32 cards
2) 4 players
3) each player is dealt 8 cards
4) top player starts the game***
5) trump suit is clubs by default at the start of the game
6) after first trick, each player assigned his own trump suit
7) each player should play card with same suit as the first played one, unless he has no card with such a suit
8) Jacks should always be tretaed as trumps

